{"tid":1005360,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇canon出部入門版嘅EOS R ?","createTime":"2019-02-02T07:17:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T06:37:32.000Z","uid":30743,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"183c97ccb3b33c8a6a67b6f2ab4b154a4c6e0102","tid":1005360,"uid":30743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T07:17:41.000Z","msg":"牙膏擠多左要收番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"198eee47b97b2bd6e0bfe0733842f458dd8e5957","tid":1005360,"uid":30743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T07:34:46.000Z","msg":"繼早前傳出 Fujifilm 將於 2 月 14 日發表新一代的 X-T30 之後，Canon 據聞亦會在同一日出手，發表經已傳了好一陣子的入門版 EOS R 全片幅無反。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，新機的型號為 EOS RP，如果以 EOS 單反作為比較的話，相信會是屬於類似 6D 系列的定位，某程度相機於操控及性能上會有一定的取捨。"},{"pid":"d9a600aeb58cc3d3c8123a8c64e7e5fc2869a49f","tid":1005360,"uid":10152,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T16:16:39.000Z","msg":"無計 商業決定<br />\n<br />\n唔會為左對家部無反 出一部全能FF Mirrorless <br />\n<br />\n咁樣只會打殘翻自己建立左咁多年既單反市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n幻想下 佢一出就出部高像素五軸防震 + 4K60p 咁佢建立既<br />\n<br />\n拍片（1DXii 條line）同 Wedding果邊5D4條line就撞晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一定會慢慢shift 過去 <br />\n<br />\n等唔切就可以買其他牌子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f31dc917d2bbc9aec5b343b330fffc30b4ec88b4","tid":1005360,"uid":1748,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"d9a600aeb58cc3d3c8123a8c64e7e5fc2869a49f","tid":1005360,"uid":10152,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T16:16:39.000Z","msg":"無計 商業決定<br />\n<br />\n唔會為左對家部無反 出一部全能FF Mirrorless <br />\n<br />\n咁樣只會打殘翻自己建立左咁多年既單反市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n幻想下 佢一出就出部高像素五軸防震 + 4K60p 咁佢建立既<br />\n<br />\n拍片（1DXii 條line）同 Wedding果邊5D4條line就撞晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一定會慢慢shift 過去 <br